{
  "page": "Feature quote/156",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Was it one of your eyes <a href=\"/index.php/Lucerys_Velaryon\" title=\"Lucerys Velaryon\">he</a> took, or one of your balls? I am <i>so</i> glad you chose my sister. I want a husband with all his parts.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Maris_Baratheon\" title=\"Maris Baratheon\">Maris Baratheon</a> to Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - A Son for a Son.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404155406\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.046 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 111/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 454/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 219/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 695/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   17.398      1 -total\n 65.66%   11.424      1 Template:Ref\n 33.68%    5.860      1 Template:References\n 33.39%    5.809      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\